{"id":6180,"date":"2023-03-02T05:28:00","date_gmt":"2023-03-02T05:28:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/?p=6180"},"modified":"2023-04-05T21:12:19","modified_gmt":"2023-04-05T21:12:19","slug":"gelar-karya-profil-pelajar-pancasila","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/2023\/03\/02\/gelar-karya-profil-pelajar-pancasila\/","title":{"rendered":"Gelar Karya &#8220;Profil Pelajar Pancasila&#8221; tentang Stop Bullying"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Peserta didik kelas X disibukan dengan gelar karya Penguatan Profil Pelajar Pancasila pada kurikulum merdeka belajar. Tak disangka karya yang mereka buat sangat di luar dugaan.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di antaranya ada yang membuat buku novel tentang bullying dengan persiapan hanya dua minggu mereka mampu membuat ratusan halaman. Ini tentu sangat luar biasa. Ujar Ibu Kepala Sekolah saat menjamu tamu studi banding.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Karya yang dihasilkan di antaranya, film pendek, lagu, lukisan, novel, popup dll.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"http:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/332876979_918012122680363_7017234720472197846_n-800x800.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"6181\" data-full-url=\"http:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/332876979_918012122680363_7017234720472197846_n.jpg\" data-link=\"http:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/?attachment_id=6181#main\" class=\"wp-image-6181\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/332876979_918012122680363_7017234720472197846_n-800x800.jpg 800w, https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/332876979_918012122680363_7017234720472197846_n-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/332876979_918012122680363_7017234720472197846_n-280x280.jpg 280w, https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/332